			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="load WLD_Main_A&#xD;&#xA;oe Denraiddone&#xD;&#xA;goto 203.57; 36.686; 441.315 , talk to arka.&#xD;&#xA;goto 187.8; 21.781; 599.34, wait for captured goblins to trigger.   &#xD;&#xA;choose the option to stand between them and end the cinematic. &#xD;&#xA;Speak to Arka as she is walking away ." />
			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="6562" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="Arka and Memnos are idle in the druid grove after going to confront the captive goblin Sazza. The goblin may or may not have been killed in this prior scene. Arka remains bitter over the recent death of their friend, Kagha, while Memnos, if present, tries to shake her out of it." />
